# Optional env file for the root bin/symphony launcher.
#
# By default the launcher resolves this file with the 1Password CLI (`op run`), so `op://`
# references are appropriate here. If you do not use 1Password, export the same variables in your
# shell and pass `--no-env-file` to the launcher instead.
LINEAR_API_KEY=op://<vault>/<item>/<field>

# Optional: if your workflow filters to one assignee.
# LINEAR_ASSIGNEE=op://<vault>/<item>/<field>

# Optional non-secret defaults. The repo-owned launcher infers these when omitted.
# SYMPHONY_DEV_ROOT=/path/to/projects
# SYMPHONY_HOME=/path/to/symphony/elixir
# SYMPHONY_LOGS_ROOT=/path/to/symphony/elixir/log

# Optional direct server port override. Leave unset to use workflow runtime.server.port.
# SYMPHONY_PORT=4000
